Wladimir Yordanoff https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wladimir_Yordanoff 0 Wladimir Yordanoff (Bulgarian: Владимир Йорданов; born 28 March 1954) is a French actor of Bulgarian origin. He has appeared in more than sixty films since 1979. Wladimir_Yordanoff ( Bulgarian : Владимир_Йорданов ; born_28_March_1954 ) is a_French_actor of Bulgarian_origin . He has_appeared in more_than_sixty_films since 1979 .
